Description: New ASN 9874 and 65010 added. New IP range 103.231.49.128/26 added.
New ASN 22870 for Syniverse GRX migration is added.
ASN 38322 is added. New IP Range 42.153.1.0/24 is added.

New ASN 131591 added. While waiting for the next new schema version 9.2 to be ready, ASN 131591 is added to Additional
Information field in Routing section.
New IP Range 103.231.48.128/26 is added. Note: Only applicable when StarHub is HPMN.
Info for second IMSI range 525-08 (SGPMM) is removed.

New IP Range 199.255.4.0/24 added. Note: IP add 199.255.4.0/24 ,116.68.0.16/28 and 116.68.0.32/28 are only applicable
when StarHub is HPMN.
StarHub introduced 2nd IMSI range and TADIG code (M2M roaming).
